#tooltuesday 🧰
-
We make a lot of signs and go through a lot of glue. We’ve tried a lot of different brands, some good, some not so good. For the last year we have transitioned to @starbondadhesives and haven’t looked back. The quality and variety they offer is uncompareable. For our signs, we prefer their clear medium CA glue. It’s not too drippy, that it will make a mess, and not too thick that it will float your layers.
-
If you haven’t tried @starbondadhesives CA glue, give them a try! It’s well worth the money and their customer service is awesome. 😁🤙🏽
